  33→ * 7. Renames files and folders
  34→ * 8. Cleans up
  35→ * 9. Logs out
  36→ *
  37→ * This approach tests a realistic user workflow with:
  38→ * - Nested folder structure (workspace/documents, workspace/images, workspace/projects/active, etc.)
