 524→  // ============================================
 525→  // After page.reload(), Zustand store is empty. The app must
 526→  // re-authenticate, re-sync root metadata from IPNS, and then
 527→  // cold-load subfolder contents via navigateTo (IPNS resolve +
 528→  // key unwrapping). This path is NOT exercised by in-session tests.
